edu.smcm.ai.tictactoe

Class TicTacToeGame

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.smcm.ai.search.AdversarialGame
      • edu.smcm.ai.tictactoe.TicTacToeGame

  • public class TicTacToeGame
extends AdversarialGame
    Implementation of the Tic Tac Toe game. The game is implemented so that is can be played on a board of any size. The number of marks that need to be in a line is the same as the size of the board. Most of the game is actually implemented in @see TicTacToeState. The size of the board is a pass-through.
